data.description: Don't miss out on this recently renovated, three bedroom, two bath all brick ranch home on a cul-de-sac lot in the sought after neighborhood of Oakpark. This community is within walking distance to the McDonough?square.?It is an open floorplan with vaulted ceilings in the dining room and great room. The hardwood floors throughout the entire home are in great condition. There are new stainless steel appliances as well as a new washer and dryer - all of this is staying with the home. The HVAC system and hot water heater are both new, as well as the light fixtures.?The entire house was recently painted and plantation shutters were installed. There is a deck overlooking the beautifully landscaped backyard which is fenced in and private.?There is an attic in the garage with steps leading up to it. This one will not last long!
